                        <p>How to use S.O.S. : </p> 
                        <ol type="1">
						<li>Create an account. </li>
						<li> If you feel unsafe, click the "activate" button. It has a countdown of 10 minutes. </li>
						<li> If you need extra time, click the "extend time" button which will add another 10 minutes to the countdown.</li>
						<li> If you do not click the "I'm safe" button and the timer reaches 0:00, it will notify both your emergency contact and the police.</li>
						<li> If S.O.S. is no longer needed, click the "I'm Safe" button.</li>
						</ol>
						
				 
           
